tieBreakingRule.text:
In the event that two (or more) teams have an equal number of points, the following rules break the tie:
1. Goal difference
2. Goals scored

tieBreakingRule.text:
In the event that two (or more) teams have an equal number of points, the following rules break the tie:

1. Head-to-head if all tied teams have paired matches
2. Goal difference
3. Goals scored

In the event that two (or more) teams have an equal number of points, the following rules break the tie:
1. Goal difference
2. Goals scored
In the event that two (or more) teams have an equal number of points, the following rules break the tie:  1. Head-to-head if all tied teams have internal matches 2. Goal difference 3. Goals scored
In the event that two (or more) teams finish with an equal number of points, the following rules break the tie: 1. Goal difference 2. Goals scored 3. Head-to-head
